          <p class="text-base text-white leading-relaxed mb-4">
            In today's data-driven business environment, organizations generate and manage unprecedented volumes of documents. Studies show that knowledge workers spend up to <strong class="text-primary">30% of their workday</strong> searching for information across scattered document repositories. This inefficiency costs businesses an estimated <strong class="text-primary">$31,000 per employee annually</strong> in lost productivity, according to IDC research.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-base text-white leading-relaxed">
            AI document management systems represent a revolutionary approach to solving these challenges, leveraging artificial intelligence to automatically organize, classify, and retrieve documents with human-like understanding and contextual awareness.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- What is AI Document Management System -->
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-6">What is AI document management system?</h2>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div>
              <p class="text-white leading-relaxed mb-4">
                An AI document management system is an intelligent software platform that uses machine learning, natural language processing, and computer vision to automatically organize, classify, and retrieve documents without human intervention. Unlike traditional document management systems that rely on manual tagging and folder structures, AI-powered solutions understand document content, context, and relationships.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-white leading-relaxed">
                These systems employ advanced technologies including <strong class="text-primary">optical character recognition (OCR)</strong>, <strong class="text-primary">semantic search capabilities</strong>, and <strong class="text-primary">automated metadata extraction</strong> to create self-organizing digital repositories that improve over time through continuous learning.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <img 
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/7679562/pexels-photo-7679562.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=300&w=500" 
                alt="Business professionals discussing AI document management implementation" 
                class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-xl border border-primary"
              />
              <p class="text-xs text-white mt-2">Strategic planning for AI document management implementation</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-primary border-l-4 border-primary p-6 rounded-r-xl mb-8">
