            <ul class="text-white space-y-2">
              <li><strong class="text-primary">Natural Language Processing (NLP):</strong> Understands document content and context</li>
              <li><strong class="text-primary">Machine Learning Algorithms:</strong> Improves classification accuracy over time</li>
              <li><strong class="text-primary">Computer Vision:</strong> Processes images, charts, and visual document elements</li>
              <li><strong class="text-primary">Semantic Search:</strong> Finds documents based on meaning, not just keywords</li>
