          <div class="space-y-8">
            <!-- Legal Firms -->
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-4">Legal Firms & Contract Management</h3>
              <p class="text-white leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Law firms handling thousands of contracts, case files, and legal precedents benefit enormously from AI document management. The system can instantly identify contract clauses, extract key terms, flag potential compliance issues, and connect related cases across decades of legal documentation.
              </p>
              
              <div class="bg-black p-4 rounded-lg">
                <p class="text-sm text-white italic">
                  "Our AI document system reduced contract review time from 4 hours to 30 minutes while improving accuracy. We can now handle 3x more cases with the same team." - Senior Partner, AmLaw 200 Firm
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Healthcare -->
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-4">Healthcare & Patient Records</h3>
              <p class="text-white leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Healthcare organizations must manage complex patient records, medical imaging, research data, and compliance documentation. AI systems can automatically extract patient information, identify treatment patterns, flag drug interactions, and ensure HIPAA compliance across all documentation.
              </p>
              
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4">
